  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the decrease of post-operative morbidity in inguinal
      lymphadenectomies realised for vulvar tumors and inferior limb skin tumors by use of
      Ultracision with regard to classical operative techniques.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
